description:
This protocol is intended as a guide for technical support units submitting milestone drafts of the assessment to the IPBES Secretariat. 
 This protocol has been prepared based on the requirements articulated in the IPBES data and knowledge management policy (https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3551078) and the set of technical guidelines (https://ict.ipbes.net/data-management/technical-guidelines) prepared by the IPBES task force on data and knowledge management. The protocol should be reviewed and applied by the assessment technical support unit prior to the submission of each milestone.&nbsp; 
 The IPBES technical support unit for data and knowledge managmenet will review and update this protocol on a regular basis. 
 &nbsp;

